{
  "id": "602b6e7aa7a61800366fa6c2",
  "title": "「考える」って何だ？",
  "created": 1613459069,
  "updated": 1613499197,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "602b6e7aa7a61800366fa6c2",
      "text": "「考える」って何だ？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459069,
      "updated": 1613459069
    },
    {
      "id": "602b6e7de5172d0000978c07",
      "text": "\t[論理的思考]、[論理的推論]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459069,
      "updated": 1613459302
    },
    {
      "id": "602b71b3e5172d00005ab874",
      "text": " \t[演繹]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459890,
      "updated": 1613459890
    },
    {
      "id": "602b71b3e5172d00005ab875",
      "text": " \t\t法則と前提条件（仮定）から、結論を導く",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459890,
      "updated": 1613460901
    },
    {
      "id": "602b71b3e5172d00005ab876",
      "text": "\t \t\t[\" 雨がふると芝生は湿る。雨がふっている。したがって、芝生は湿っている。]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459890,
      "updated": 1613460171
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7518e5172d00005ab88a",
      "text": "\t \t\t[三段論法]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613460759,
      "updated": 1613460765
    },
    {
      "id": "602c06861280f000008a426d",
      "text": "\t \t\t [仮定除去]を二回用いて導出する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613497990,
      "updated": 1613498033
    },
    {
      "id": "602b71b7e5172d00005ab877",
      "text": " \t\t数学者？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459895,
      "updated": 1613460741
    },
    {
      "id": "602c06021280f000008a426b",
      "text": " \t\t 数学者は当然使うけど、数学者と結びつけると視野がせばまる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613497858,
      "updated": 1613497908
    },
    {
      "id": "602c06351280f000008a426c",
      "text": " \t\t 何らかの研究をしている人は全員これを使っているはず",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613497909,
      "updated": 1613497956
    },
    {
      "id": "602b6ea9e5172d0000978c0a",
      "text": " \t[帰納]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459113,
      "updated": 1613459395
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7085e5172d00005ab872",
      "text": " \t\t前提条件と結論の事例集から、法則を学ぶ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459589,
      "updated": 1613460891
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7248e5172d00005ab87d",
      "text": " \t\t\t[\" これまで、雨がふるといつも芝生は湿ってきた。したがって、雨がふると芝生は湿る。]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613460039,
      "updated": 1613460169
    },
    {
      "id": "602b71c4e5172d00005ab878",
      "text": " \t\t科学者？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459907,
      "updated": 1613460742
    },
    {
      "id": "602c06be1280f000008a426e",
      "text": " \t\t過去の経験から未来を予測する手法",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498046,
      "updated": 1613498086
    },
    {
      "id": "602c06e71280f000008a426f",
      "text": " \t\tほぼすべての人間が使っている",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498087,
      "updated": 1613498118
    },
    {
      "id": "602c07071280f000008a4270",
      "text": " \t\t 世界の根本法則がわからない以上、事例から推測するしかない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498119,
      "updated": 1613498153
    },
    {
      "id": "602c07291280f000008a4271",
      "text": " \t\t 法則は既知だが厳密解の導出が困難な場合にも使用される",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498153,
      "updated": 1613498270
    },
    {
      "id": "602b6fc4e5172d00005ab86f",
      "text": " \t[仮説形成]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459395,
      "updated": 1613462645
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7c76e5172d00005ab8b1",
      "text": " \t\t[abduction]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613462645,
      "updated": 1613462645
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7294e5172d00005ab881",
      "text": " \t\t事象を最も適切に説明しうる[仮説]を導出する論理的推論",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613460115,
      "updated": 1613460140
    },
    {
      "id": "602b72b9e5172d00005ab884",
      "text": " \t\t結論と法則から、前提条件（原因）を推定する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613460153,
      "updated": 1613461173
    },
    {
      "id": "602b72c7e5172d00005ab886",
      "text": " \t\t\t[\" 芝生が湿っている。雨がふると芝生が湿る。したがって、雨がふったに違いない。]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613460167,
      "updated": 1613460168
    },
    {
      "id": "602b767ae5172d00005ab89c",
      "text": " \t\t\tプログラムの[デバッグ]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461113,
      "updated": 1613461135
    },
    {
      "id": "602b75ede5172d00005ab896",
      "text": "\t\t\t結論や法則についての仮説を推定することを言うこともある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613460973,
      "updated": 1613461222
    },
    {
      "id": "602c07d11280f000008a4273",
      "text": "\t\t\t[あたりをつけ]るという語はこのことを示しているといえそう[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498320,
      "updated": 1613498372
    },
    {
      "id": "602c07ac1280f000008a4272",
      "text": "\t\t\t実際に正しいかは演繹して確認する必要がある",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498283,
      "updated": 1613498404
    },
    {
      "id": "602b760fe5172d00005ab89b",
      "text": " \t\t歴史科学者、診断専門医、探偵",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461006,
      "updated": 1613461006
    },
    {
      "id": "602b772fe5172d00005ab8a1",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%A2%E3%83%96%E3%83%80%E3%82%AF%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%B3 アブダクション - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461294,
      "updated": 1613461294
    },
    {
      "id": "602b772fe5172d00005ab8a2",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AB%96%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A8%E8%AB%96 論理的推論 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461294,
      "updated": 1613461294
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7ea6e5172d00005ab8b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613463205,
      "updated": 1613463205
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7ea7e5172d00005ab8ba",
      "text": "\t[最尤推定]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613463206,
      "updated": 1613463206
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7ea7e5172d00005ab8bb",
      "text": "\t[ベイズ推定]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613463206,
      "updated": 1613463206
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7731e5172d00005ab8a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461296,
      "updated": 1613461296
    },
    {
      "id": "602b6f06e5172d0000978c11",
      "text": "\t[アナロジー]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459206,
      "updated": 1613462664
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7c89e5172d00005ab8b2",
      "text": "\t\t[類推]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613462664,
      "updated": 1613462664
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7753e5172d00005ab8a6",
      "text": "\t\t>特定の事物に基づく情報を、他の特定の事物へ、それらの間の何らかの類似に基づいて適用する認知過程",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461330,
      "updated": 1613461365
    },
    {
      "id": "602b77a3e5172d00005ab8a8",
      "text": "\t\t[意思決定]、説明（[例え]話とか）、科学理論の形成、芸術家の[創造]作業",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461410,
      "updated": 1613499197
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7846e5172d00005ab8ad",
      "text": "\t\t論理的に正しいとは限らない",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461573,
      "updated": 1613461584
    },
    {
      "id": "602b78bfe5172d00005ab8ae",
      "text": "\t\t日常生活での「理解」はだいたいこれな気がする[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461694,
      "updated": 1613461708
    },
    {
      "id": "602c083f1280f000008a4274",
      "text": "\t\t研究もこれが重要だと思う[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498430,
      "updated": 1613498464
    },
    {
      "id": "602c08611280f000008a4275",
      "text": "\t\t 知識と知識を結びつけて、背景にある原理を探る",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498465,
      "updated": 1613498500
    },
    {
      "id": "602c08851280f000008a4276",
      "text": "\t\t  [抽象化]ともいう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498500,
      "updated": 1613499182
    },
    {
      "id": "602c08961280f000008a4277",
      "text": "\t\t 普段から他分野の情報に触れておくと、別分野との共通点を見つけたり、他分野の手法を自分の分野に取り入れるという発想が浮かんだりしてとても役に立つし楽しい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1613498518,
      "updated": 1613498741
    },
    {
      "id": "602c0ad3e5172d00001495dc",
      "text": "\t\t経験のない状況に遭遇したときに役立つ[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613499089,
      "updated": 1613499135
    },
    {
      "id": "602c0af9e5172d00001495dd",
      "text": "\t\t\t既存の知識を[応用]できる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613499128,
      "updated": 1613499178
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7e54e5172d00005ab8b8",
      "text": "\t[共感]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613463124,
      "updated": 1613463127
    },
    {
      "id": "602b6f0de5172d0000978c13",
      "text": "\t[直観]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459212,
      "updated": 1613462623
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7c61e5172d00005ab8b0",
      "text": "\t\tIntuition",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613462624,
      "updated": 1613462631
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7c8de5172d00005ab8b3",
      "text": "\t\t熟知している領域で、推論や類推などをせずに、瞬時に理解できること",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613462668,
      "updated": 1613462776
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7d62e5172d00005ab8b4",
      "text": "\t\t多くの経験（による知識と理解）が必要",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613462881,
      "updated": 1613462889
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7d7ee5172d00005ab8b5",
      "text": "\t\t>直感とは感覚的に物事を感じとることで、勘（で答える）のような日常会話での用語を指す",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613462910,
      "updated": 1613462911
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7d97e5172d00005ab8b6",
      "text": "\t\t\t何が違うのかわからん[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613462934,
      "updated": 1613462946
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7dd6e5172d00005ab8b7",
      "text": "\t[洞察]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613462998,
      "updated": 1613463000
    },
    {
      "id": "602b77b3e5172d00005ab8ac",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A1%9E%E6%8E%A8 類推 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461426,
      "updated": 1613461428
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7c4be5172d00005ab8af",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%9B%B4%E8%A6%B3 直観 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613462603,
      "updated": 1613462603
    },
    {
      "id": "602b6eb8e5172d0000978c0b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459128,
      "updated": 1613459128
    },
    {
      "id": "602b6fbae5172d00005ab86e",
      "text": "\t[メタ認知]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613459386,
      "updated": 1613463220
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7eb6e5172d00005ab8bc",
      "text": "\t[客観視]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613463221,
      "updated": 1613463285
    },
    {
      "id": "602b7734e5172d00005ab8a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1613461300,
      "updated": 1613461300
    }
  ]
}